Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 那时 那个雨天..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 抱歉 让我稍微躲会儿雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想挨打
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 到处都充斥着疼痛和恐惧 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静下心来再想怎么做 全都归你 还是全都给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你想怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由诧 佳奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫一马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有姓 只有名字一马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个小鬼别直呼我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 因为叫一马 就喊一君好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么叫 那啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我这样祈望着 希望这一刻能成为永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着粗鲁的他的侧脸 不自禁如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}抓紧心中的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}即使被绝望和失望打垮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}最后仍会站起来 独自的Glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}不能逃避的 Battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}将足迹向下一个地点延伸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}即使把白色的地图染成红色也要前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}风险和不利是导火索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,400)}将兴奋的“确信”之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}射向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Reckless fire 如此大胆地 磨练生命之术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}这个世界是生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}无论白与黑所走的路只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}不可能熄灭 此刻心中的篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}希望能贯彻坚定不移的本能与意志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(380,450,470,455,0,1750)}{\fad(1500,1000)}由詑 佳奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 稍微好吃点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 还那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真让人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈美 之前怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和刘凤那个男人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我.. 一君和刘凤战斗的时候 我..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刘凤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一马
